erson: At your local Veteran Affairs Medical Center’s Agent 
Cashier’s Office
By Phone: Contact VA at 1-888-827-4817
Online: Pay by ACH withdrawal from your bank account, or 
by debit or credit card at www.pay.gov
By Mail: Make check or money order payable to “VA” and include 
account number and payment stub. Submit to: Department of Veterans Affairs, P.O. Box 530269, Atlanta, GA 30353-0269
